strings: <voice_0x0100095A><se_low>*: Well, well! You must be really brave to come up and talk to me like this!
<voice_0x0100095B><se_low>*: A man that looked like a peddler came along earlier, but when he saw me he ran away without saying a word!
<voice_0x0100095C><se_low>*: Anyway... As you've probably realised, you'll have to fight me if you want to go any further!

<voice_0x0100095D><se_low>*: What do you think?
Brave enough for that, are you!?
<voice_0x01000963><se_low>*: I thought as much!
<voice_0x01000964><se_low>*: Then you'd better be on your way.

<voice_0x01000965><se_low>*: Hm? What do you want now?
Have you changed your mind about fighting me?

<voice_0x0100095E><se_low>*: R-Really!? Y-You are brave.
That means you must be a good fighter...

<voice_0x01000961><se_low>*: I know! In recognition of your bravery,
I'm going to let you through!

<voice_0x01000962><se_low>*: Off you go.
Be careful now!
<voice_0x01000966><se_low>*: Do you, by any chance, think I'm a bit of a wimp? Well, I'm not, I tell you!
<voice_0x01000967><se_low>*: If you don't believe me, why don't you try your luck and fight me!?
<voice_0x01000969><se_low>*: Oh, r-really...!?
<voice_0x0100096A><se_low>*: Th-Then I suppose that's decided. Let's fight!
<voice_0x0100096B><se_low>*: Y-You caught me off guard. Uuurgh...

<voice_0x0100096C><se_low>*: But I suppose you won fair and square.
Go on, you can pass.
<voice_0x0100096D><se_low>*: A-ha! You again! You do remember how strong I am, right?

<voice_0x0100096E><se_low>*: So what's the verdict?
Do you want a rematch!?

<voice_0x01000968><se_low>*: Then off you go.
Be careful now!
